              {
                "text": "Do not walk, swim, or drive through flood waters. Never cross any barriers that are put in place by emergency officials. You likely will not know the depth of the water or the condition of the ground. Road beds may be washed out under flood waters."
              }
            ],
            "response_type": "text",
            "selection_policy": "sequential"
          }
        ]
      },
      "conditions": "#Flood_Travel",
      "dialog_node": "node_7_1584394345975",
